data.description: Welcome to Norfolk! This centrally located property gives you quick access to the Norfolk International Airport, Zoo, Botanical Gardens, Norfolk Naval base, Norfolk Premium Outlets and many more attractions! The 2 car driveway and wide street offers ample parking. In the large backyard you can enjoy your spacious patio deck for entertaining. Inside offers floor to ceiling kitchen cabinetry, 3 first floor bedrooms including a primary suite, and a large upstairs loft area that could be converted to functional living space or extra storage needs.
